    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "次は事務所で雑誌の取材か……\n最近こんな仕事ばかりで嫌になっちゃうよね、莉央",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Next is a magazine interview at the office…\nI’m getting sick of all these jobs lately‚ Rio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.973741626739502,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5466.666666666667,
          "startTime": 6.266666666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "莉央？\nそんなに真剣に何を観てるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio?\nWhat are you watching so seriously?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.166666666666668,
      "endTime": 11.741745917002362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.166666666666671
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4の動画よ\nVENUSプログラムの頂点にいる4グループ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a BIG4 video.\nThe four groups at the top of the VENUS program.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.933333333333332,
      "endTime": 17.149387582143145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.333333333333286
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりすごいわ……\n観客の熱狂振りが怖いくらいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re amazing…\nThe audience’s enthusiasm is frightening.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.33333333333333,
      "endTime": 21.77439893086751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.9743989308675
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "確かに歌もダンスも凄いけど……\n僕はこの子達にも負ける気はしないね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The singing and dancing are amazing‚ but…\n…I don’t think I’d lose to these girls.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.9743989308675,
      "endTime": 28.47439874013264,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "葵はBIG4に対してまで強気なのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re being bold even against BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.674398930867493,
      "endTime": 31.574398835500066,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.674398930867522
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "この子達の勢いは\nあの時の長瀬麻奈と同じくらいだと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The momentum of these girls…\n…is about the same as Mana Nagase back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.774398835500065,
      "endTime": 36.474398930867494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "長瀬麻奈……\n三枝さんが見いだした天才アイドル……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana Nagase…\n…The genius idol that Saegusa-san discovered…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.67439883550008,
      "endTime": 41.40773216883339,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.6743988355001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "僕達はその長瀬麻奈に勝つんだよね？\nだから、この子達にだって負けるつもりはないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re going to beat that Mana Nagase‚ right?\nSo‚ I’m not going to lose to these girls either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.67439883550008,
      "endTime": 49.00936482747395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.6743988355001
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.274398835500065
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.274398835500065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03-mna009.m4a",
      "text": "そうやって私に勝つって言ってきた人達は\n一杯いたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’ve been a lot of people\nwho told me they would beat me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.3077321688334,
      "endTime": 55.53185927073159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.741065502166734
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_02_03-mna010.m4a",
      "text": "でも私だって負けるつもりはないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I don’t plan on losing either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.741065502166734,
      "endTime": 58.98315172195433,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.07439883550005
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.07439883550005
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "……そうね\nそうだったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Right.\nThat’s right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.24106550216673,
      "endTime": 63.61201791763303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "私達にあんな捨て台詞を吐いて\n勝手に逝ってしまったあの子……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That girl who said those harsh words to us\n…and then left us…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8077321688334,
      "endTime": 68.36294781366982,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.74106550216672
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "……勝ち逃げなんて許さないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I won’t forgive her for running away like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.74106550216672,
      "endTime": 70.87439883550005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "次のNEXT VENUSグランプリは\n私達が……LizNoirが優勝してみせる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We…\n…LizNoir will win!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.17439883550006,
      "endTime": 77.54811786015826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.1743988355001
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.7410655021667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "優勝じゃない\n圧勝だよ、莉央",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not win‚\n…landslide victory‚ Rio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.7410655021667,
      "endTime": 81.2844441413879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.48750015405504
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "たとえ長瀬麻奈が生きていたとしても\n僕達の方が上だと証明するんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if Mana Nagase were still alive‚\nwe’d still be better. We’ll prove it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.48750015405504,
      "endTime": 87.0607202163109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、絶対に勝ちましょう、葵",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ let’s definitely win‚ Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.26895437571898,
      "endTime": 90.51503148410215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.71503148410206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "うん、僕達なら勝てる\n僕と莉央なら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ we can win.\nRio and I.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.71503148410216,
      "endTime": 95.62670960757627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.8150314841021
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、頼もしいパートナーで嬉しい\n……あ、もうこんな時間だわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I’m happy to have such a reliable partner.\n…Ah‚ it’s already this late.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.8150314841021,
      "endTime": 102.08376145694145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.71503148410216
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "早く事務所に戻りましょう\n姫野さんが待っているわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s hurry back to the office.\nHimeno-san will be waiting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.38169815076883,
      "endTime": 106.02267319692668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.21503148410218
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_03_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "雑誌の記者さんと一緒にね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Together with the magazine reporter.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.21503148410218,
      "endTime": 109.16503157946963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
